			subtitle: "This is a major milestone! You've discovered a way to convert Rotational Energy into electricity! However, the Alternating Dynamo is a pretty primitive way of obtaining electricity, so it might be necessary to make more then one of these to power your machines, as it has a maximum output of 128 RF/tick and that will be achieved by constantly consuming 4,096 SU"
