			x: 4.0d
			y: -8.0d
			shape: "diamond"
			subtitle: "The Electrolyzed Alloy is a highly conductive material which can be charged up with electricity. It CANNOT be used as a battery, but when it's Overcharged, it becomes a material used in lots of recipes. It needs 19200 RF in order to become Overcharged. Also, the process takes around 30 seconds. This amount of time CANNOT be reduced by any means"
