		{
			x: -5.5d
			y: -2.5d
			shape: "gear"
			subtitle: "A turtle can be upgraded with certain tools to create a mini-robot. Turtles can be programmed through the lua language to do lots of things, such as, mob grinders, quarrys and more. You can take a look at the \"Useful Items\" tab to see more about the turtles you can use"
			dependencies: ["2CBD58CB08491491"]
